thread.title: David and Josephine
thread.title_full: buyMyplace reviewed by David and Josephine

author: David and Josephine
title: David and Josephine
text:
Our local Real Estate agents could not sell our country property in 18 months. We started to wonder if it would ever selll.
We decided to try Buy my place and were able to take charge of selling our own property. We have saved a small fortune and are very happy to recommend 'Buy my Place!
Dave and Josie N
